display_long_description:
Think you’ve got what it takes? Spoiler: No one has ever cleared all the levels! Countless players took one look at these 4-piece puzzles and thought, "How hard could it be?" Every single one of them underestimated  Cube Master—and found themselves hopelessly hooked, if not completely outsmarted.

**Developer's Note:**
IMPORTANT WARNING: I do not recommend anyone to start the game on Hard mode, because it is so damn hard, if you don't believe me, you may regret it, and please tell others in the comments not to do it. lol

Initially, the game only featured Normal and Hard modes, but many players shared their feedback about the difficulty. Enjoy

**About 600 Unique Levels:**  With About 600 meticulously crafted puzzles, each level is a new journey that will keep you challenged, entertained, and determined.

**Minimal Pieces, Maximum Fun:** Each level may only use up to 4 blocks, but don't let that fool you. Some levels are quick and breezy, while others will twist your mind, leaving even the boldest players stumped!

**Fun for All Players:** Designed with varying levels of difficulty. Regardless of your skill, there's a level waiting to challenge you.

**Immersive Puzzle Experience:** Even a mere 4-piece puzzle can be surprisingly complex, keeping you engaged—and sometimes stuck—for up to half an hour on a single level!

Dare to think it’s simple? Test your wits in Cube Master—if you’re ready for the ultimate puzzle challenge!
